docs {
**List Message Receipts**
Paginated list of the message's per-channel delivery receipts (read-only).

HTTP Basic Auth: username = `{{accountSid}}`, password = `{{apiKey}}`.

OperationId: `conversations.v1.conversations.messages.receipts.list`
}
